+  ShouldCreateBucket1: !Equals
+    - !Ref AWS::AccountId
+    - 123456789012
+  ShouldCreateBucket2: !Equals
+    - !Ref AWS::AccountId
+    - 234567890123
+  ShouldCreateBucket3: !Equals
+    - !Ref AWS::AccountId
